  "body": "<div class=\"se-main-container\">\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-2068f162-2727-4fc5-8be7-46d12c420064\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-9a6adf57-bab9-4670-ab4d-cacd4c1b4a41\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-0d29c054-a432-4be6-ae06-b8970870c946\"><b>안녕하세요 몸과 마음을 건강하게 </b></span><span style=\"background-color:#ffef34;\" class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-b2f79e07-124c-44ea-b6ce-88756f4d8404\"><b>이수한의원</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-7d1b75a4-696a-4bee-84ee-d29fa377ba2d\"><b> 입니다!</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-2068f162-2727-4fc5-8be7-46d12c420064\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-sticker se-l-default\" id=\"SE-2f89c478-fead-4c54-8ee1-62373d3666a3\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-sticker se-section-align-center se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-sticker\">\n                                <a href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" class=\"__se_sticker_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"sticker\" data-linkdata='{\"src\" : \"\", \"packCode\" : \"motion2d_01\", \"seq\" : \"7\", \"width\" : \"\", \"height\" : \"\"}'>\n                                    <img src=\"https://storep-phinf.pstatic.net/motion2d_01/original_7.png?type=p100_100\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-sticker-image\" />\n                                </a>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-2410ad29-53ca-4be4-b2c5-d6b5f9771952\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-7d3c0e68-12e9-40ac-a6df-67dd44ad3eb9\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-c93a8379-612f-49af-ba89-0c7de8fcb6e9\"><b> &quot;속이 더부룩해요…&quot;</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-80eb81e1-8ba7-4f64-9931-0ab15f830fd0\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-93493114-e284-4557-a981-00275c2b6556\">소화가 안 돼서 더부룩하거나 트림, 속쓰림, 가스 참 같은 증상이 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-b1fcc10f-5343-414c-8f45-66ba7f9cc617\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-48dd535c-830f-4c0f-ba02-0e07c7b0c58b\">자주 반복되시나요?</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-39b2a6da-253b-4fc1-8cd3-ece6967ebee7\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-bb219b08-607b-4561-8029-1bd28ed3fb55\">이럴 때 많은 분들이 약만 찾기 쉬운데요, 한의학에서는 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-83a2753c-04ae-4461-a7d9-22f9a99f03b0\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-5ec82b9c-4746-4d73-a0f9-582a29268e12\">우리 몸에 있는 혈자리(경혈)를 자극해</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-61ffa53c-436c-4a8c-b20d-77feebca780b\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-1c6c4b2b-9a7e-43f0-8840-2e853b3b16fc\">자연스럽게 소화를 돕는 방법도 매우 효과적이라고 봅니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-4906b5fe-80a6-44b3-81c5-065128b34b5f\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-4f9f7990-3d97-4fe1-b52b-8e0a1312a6ba\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-5d9af20c-2c91-4f61-9322-3488e7a917f1\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-ca49841c-b8e1-4677-9fae-a2c0163c2ff5\">그중에서도 </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-49b539e5-6f7d-4740-b60d-854e56dfb4ff\"><b>손과 다리에 있는 소화 관련 혈자리</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-b26192c5-1329-4266-887e-fda9a0de5a92\">는 집에서 누구나 쉽게 눌러볼 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-ae6fe748-f311-4619-8139-470d524f0bef\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-1c408fd3-cf4a-47b6-b3d0-89262795bb7d\">손과 다리 지압으로 다스리는 소화불량, </span><span style=\"background-color:#ffef34;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-642cd143-dc9e-4774-a3b6-1cc200df95c7\"><b>이수한의원</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-6c487efd-330a-4bab-a51f-d769bae2434c\">이 알려드립니다</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-2410ad29-53ca-4be4-b2c5-d6b5f9771952\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line1\" id=\"SE-ee1986f6-c518-4f69-b03f-bcdd1faf5a5e\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line1 se-section-align-\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n                                <hr class=\"se-hr\" />\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-88cb8b33-76b0-49af-b4d1-4b8ab6a781b0\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-88cb8b33-76b0-49af-b4d1-4b8ab6a781b0\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/393b4c57f5588a61.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1600\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1600\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/393b4c57f5588a61.png\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/393b4c57f5588a61.png\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"500\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_image\", \"id\": \"SE-88cb8b33-76b0-49af-b4d1-4b8ab6a781b0\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"image\", \"ai\": \"false\" }}'></script>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-e74bbc12-bd81-4015-95e6-04dbfd312b59\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-efe89e27-f08d-400a-ab07-07eb8deb7c6e\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-4772ab47-1260-4ba4-bd6f-9e65cf0c0be2\"><b>🖐 손과 다리에서 찾는 소화 지압점 3가지</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-c4b5b5b4-8e4b-48d8-8c9f-2e16b70757fd\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-05058b7f-87cd-47f5-93d9-2141817f4761\"><b>1. 합곡혈(合谷穴) – 손등의 만능 혈자리</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-0067f1ad-32f6-420a-a66b-a82e80929287\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-5a56f163-b68e-45d8-b5a5-d427aa2831bd\"><b>위치</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-abfe1930-11ab-49c0-8e7e-3c0f4a56d067\">: 엄지와 검지 뼈가 만나는 V자 부위</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-d2020510-c649-4205-8251-3565dceba0cf\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-581dfe59-a849-4758-821b-6a75b5edf39a\"><b>효과</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-c08dc9e4-b337-445e-81cc-cd506a8c81b5\">: 상체의 순환을 도와 </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-cf996f46-11c7-4e09-bee0-d9ad0060fad7\"><b>트림, 더부룩함, 체한 느낌</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-d9da1fc3-ebf3-48d3-874f-20cb6749fded\"> 완화</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-fb283e47-0025-46db-a179-626cafa4f24c\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-97db53c0-4e77-45cf-b846-5d53c2f94af6\"><b>지압법</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-982446bd-01e3-4f2e-98d8-6a403f434f4f\">: 반대 손의 엄지로 꾹 눌러 5초간 유지, 10회 반복</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-cdd85e86-1a87-45fe-8b5e-393a076658cc\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-00a94d57-abd2-4b93-aad6-ca5a7a8fdadf\"><b>Tip</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-75dcb973-082e-49c0-9ed6-465b414ab5ca\">: 배탈, 두통, 스트레스성 소화불량에도 좋아요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-e74bbc12-bd81-4015-95e6-04dbfd312b59\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line1\" id=\"SE-c7042354-3f8e-40fd-8fb0-47258fc86e4a\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line1 se-section-align-\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n                                <hr class=\"se-hr\" />\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-5a4495db-33a7-4dbc-9821-c8ed23d1e18e\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-045990a7-9f81-4259-842f-a010ebf4e864\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-e3c18b3d-1942-4863-b1cc-395b3f087203\"><b>2. 족삼리혈(足三里穴) – 위장 기능 강화의 핵심</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-f23a6abf-1826-4826-978f-a6ce986dc4f6\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-36e2472b-2d96-465a-a3f8-d410cc83380d\"><b>위치</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-3c9a8979-0446-4743-a3c7-c141ca9c49cb\">: 무릎 아래 4가락 정도 아래, 정강이 바깥쪽 오목한 곳</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-cb010b13-090a-4264-894b-670c2ce76ee6\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-1d5a92f8-3844-41a0-9c3f-adc720f385f2\"><b>효과</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-f180746a-6328-4cef-bf80-c913e24508d3\">: </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-a2723412-5ec3-47ca-8a52-f02de4f2617a\"><b>소화기능 저하, 만성 위장 장애</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-fed506e0-00ae-4726-b156-d07f7bd426c0\"> 개선</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-bde6eb5f-1897-40f2-926e-657185b9a69b\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-71f4a1f9-11b4-45dc-a8a4-943d4b57bb11\"><b>지압법</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-cc528d32-e241-490a-9172-a4ef1b1c22cc\">: 양손 엄지로 꾹 누르며 10초 유지, 좌우 번갈아 5회</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-8af11d0c-e093-486a-af70-f5cefc5abe5f\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-e79bd70e-fa80-4dbd-abfd-ece7849967a3\"><b>Tip</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-4b10f61f-00a2-4637-b3e9-16ee5d15f1e2\">: 하루 한 번씩만 지압해도 위장 기능에 도움돼요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-5a4495db-33a7-4dbc-9821-c8ed23d1e18e\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line1\" id=\"SE-85e8a30e-4e7d-400a-876b-fd71c97eb922\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line1 se-section-align-\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n                                <hr class=\"se-hr\" />\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-173e80d9-e16a-4c78-8950-3bbfe6974b78\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-6834c3f4-1ef2-403b-95f7-e6642d797d3e\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-986278af-0826-4185-909d-baba5c5e5ea1\"><b>3. 내관혈(內關穴) – 메스꺼움, 구역감 완화</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-195f51b3-9257-4aa3-8682-997ac0a0501c\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-912a93b1-e70e-4cf5-a18f-c1f67996274f\"><b>위치</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-ee1e77c8-f324-4924-8f03-902db45fdfa7\">: 손목 안쪽 주름에서 팔꿈치 쪽으로 약 3손가락 위</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-67e801b7-475a-4f13-ad64-59b198f1ff0a\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-9e2d0d8a-ac1d-4a3b-992f-6617a1126527\"><b>효과</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-4528d1bd-7f0e-401d-b315-cf4513ce6fa4\">: </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-b8db6663-aaff-4bd8-b66d-780f1a78877d\"><b>속 메스꺼움, 구토, 가슴 답답함</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-c8973256-f165-4181-a040-c666740234a7\"> 완화</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-d26c1d2e-5c9f-4a4a-a004-f825cf1a71a5\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-c1d89c1c-568c-43d6-9d35-a1e61ebc3227\"><b>지압법</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-c2482afa-c892-4d77-8494-be71d73bcf09\">: 중지나 엄지로 부드럽게 1~2분 원을 그리며 지압</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-3985e758-d9f7-4d82-bc12-29dc258bf044\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-e2c4b276-6e54-4294-bfbe-9606ef811d35\"><b>Tip</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-344fc8a4-0e0b-4e48-8b44-19a158c9a7fa\">: 멀미약 대용으로도 알려진 혈이에요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-173e80d9-e16a-4c78-8950-3bbfe6974b78\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line1\" id=\"SE-